description: With the Alexa Leap Year skill you can quickly find out if this year, or next year, or any year you give Alexa is a leap year. Never be wrong about this again with the Leap Year skill.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask leap year if this year is a leap year
name: Leap year
shortDescription: Leap Year informs you if the year you provide is a leap year or if its not.
